author: stevel
msg: experimental gump debugging. This patch goes with a gump descriptor patch  to set the property axis.lib.dir to lib, not lib.dir; we then resolve that property to lib.dir, hence forcing it to an absolute path regardless of whether it was set on the command line, in the build file as normal, or by gump.
